summary: Official Website of Karaton Surakarta Digital Token - Step into the Rediscovery of Greatness, where the lost story of Karaton Surakarta Hadiningrat, an ancient kingdom in Java, comes back to glory. Uncover tales and wisdom from a fading history, now brought back for you. On a mission to connect the past and future, using technology to make history lively and easy to explore. This isn't just a trip into the past, It's an invitation to enjoy the honorable spirit of Java.
